    ðŸ”¹ `luit -list` --> ðŸ“š Display a list of all supported encodings.

ðŸ›  **Examples:**

    $ luit program_name

    ðŸ”¹ Run `program_name` with UTF-8 encoding.

    $ luit -encoding ISO-8859-1 another_program

    ðŸ”¹ Run `another_program` with the `ISO-8859-1` encoding.

